Package: epstool
Version: 2.1
Revision: 1
BuildDepends: dlcompat-dev
Depends: ghostscript
Description: Utility to manipulate preview images in EPS files
Source: ftp://mirror.cs.wisc.edu/pub/mirrors/ghost/ghostgum/gsv42src.zip
NoSourceDirectory: true
PatchScript: <<
 unzip epstool.zip
 unzip src.zip
 patch -p0 < %a/%f.patch
<<
CompileScript: (cd epstool; make -f makefile.unx INCLUDES='-I../src -I../epstool' CC=cc)
InstallScript: <<
 mkdir -p %i/bin
 (cd epstool; make -f makefile.unx install BINDIR=%i/bin)
<<
DocFiles: LICENCE epstool/epstool.htm
License: Restrictive
Homepage: http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~ghost/gsview/epstool.htm
